'''2-乙烯基-4,6-二氨基-1,3,5-三嗪'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为(H<sub>2</sub>NC)<sub>2</sub>N<sub>3</sub>CCH=CH<sub>2</sub>，它是无色固体，是某些氢键聚合物的单体前体。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1021/ma001700r|title=Reversible Side Chain Modification through Noncovalent Interactions. "Plug and Play" Polymers|year=2001|last1=Ilhan|first1=Faysal|last2=Gray|first2=Mark|last3=Rotello|first3=Vincent M.|journal=Macromolecules|volume=34|issue=8|pages=2597–2601|bibcode=2001MaMol..34.2597I}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.reactfunctpolym.2019.01.004|title=Synthesis of poly(2-vinyl-4,6-diamino-1,3,5-triazine) nanoparticles by semi-continuous precipitation polymerization, characterization and application to bovine hemoglobin adsorption|year=2019|last1=Xie|first1=Xun|last2=Huang|first2=Lei|last3=Liu|first3=Zuifang|last4=Xie|first4=Weihong|last5=Wang|first5=Xiatao|journal=Reactive and Functional Polymers|volume=141|pages=58–67}}</ref>它和{{ld|4-溴-1,2-苯二酚|4-Brombrenzcatechin}}在钯[[催化剂|催化剂]]的存在下反应，可以得到4-[2-(4,6-二氨基-1,3,5-三嗪-2-基)乙基]-1,2-苯二酚。<ref>Tabei, Junichi. Resin composition for sealing and semiconductor device. 2016. JP 2016020464 A.</ref>
